T02TD2151E:245b-1: n'a ga ku la tsa tva ri s'a dha n'am n'a ma bod skad du /
T02TD2151E:245b-2: klu rigs bzhi'i sgrub thabs zhes bya ba /
T02TD2151E:245b-3: phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2151E:245b-4: thugs rje byams pas 'gro ba rnams lam bzhin brtse bar mdzad //
T02TD2151E:245b-5: gdug pa 'dul phyir khro rgyal 'bar ba'i skur ston pa //
T02TD2151E:245b-6: byol song rgyan ldan bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar //
T02TD2151E:245b-7: bzod dka' gdug pa'i nad las thar mdzad de la dngos po kun gyis 'dud //
T02TD2151E:245b-8: byams pas zhe sdang zhi ba dang /
T02TD2151E:245b-9: drag pos nye rings gsang ba'i phyir ;
T02TD2151E:245b-10: / de yi sgrub thabs gzung ba'i phyir //
T02TD2151E:245b-11: bla ma'i drin gyis thob nas brtsam //
T02TD2151E:245b-12: gang zhig bsnyen pa rdzogs pa yis //
T02TD2151E:245b-13: gang zhig dbang du bsdu 'dod na //
T02TD2151E:245b-15: sbyor ba brtsam par bya ba yin //
T02TD2151E:245b-16: dang po gnas chen yid 'ong du //
T02TD2151E:245b-17: bsnyen pa sngon du rdzogs byas te //
T02TD2151E:246a-1: ni 'khar gzhong gzhag / rang nyid lha yi skur bsgoms na //
T02TD2151E:246a-2: dus gsum klu la mchod pa bya //
T02TD2151E:246a-3: rtags dang rmi lam brtags nas ni //
T02TD2151E:246a-4: de las bzlog pa'i las brtsam ste //
T02TD2151E:246a-5: mtshams bcad sa yi cho ga bya //
T02TD2151E:246a-6: stegs bu byi dor legs byas te //
T02TD2151E:246a-7: sta gon cho ga rgyas byas la //
T02TD2151E:246a-8: de nas rdzas rnams bsag par bya //
T02TD2151E:246a-9: 'bras kyi rgyu las byas pa yi //
T02TD2151E:246a-10: klu chen brgyad ni sbrul mgo can //
T02TD2151E:246a-11: dngul gzhong nang du bsag par bya /
T02TD2151E:246a-12: kha dog tshon gyis bsgyur la gzhag / so so lto 'phye'i mgo bo ni //
T02TD2151E:246a-13: dgu dang bdun dang lnga dang gsum //
T02TD2151E:246a-14: skyes pa bud med mdzes pa dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-15: sbrul dang sbal pa lcong mo dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-16: nya dang rus sbal rkang mngas dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-17: sdig pa phag dang mdo rtol dre //
T02TD2151E:246a-18: gzhan yang gang byung gzugs bya'o //
T02TD2151E:246a-19: de nas thig dang chon dgye zhing //
T02TD2151E:246a-20: dbus kyi lte ba zlum po la //
T02TD2151E:246a-21: gtso bo dbus su bris nas ni //
T02TD2151E:246a-22: 'dab ma brgyad la klu brgyad bri //
T02TD2151E:246a-23: phyi rol gyi ni 'dab ma la //
T02TD2151E:246a-24: 'khor du gtogs pa so sor bri //
T02TD2151E:246a-25: shar la sogs pa'i phyogs rnams su //
T02TD2151E:246a-26: skyes pa bud med la sogs bri //
T02TD2151E:246a-27: mtshams su lcong mo nya sogs dgod//
T02TD2151E:246a-28: steng du sdig pa phag sogs bri'o //
T02TD2151E:246a-29: steng du 'khar gzhong klu chen brgyad //
T02TD2151E:246a-30: bar khyams lha yi snam bu la //
T02TD2151E:246a-31: klu dang gnyan dang sa bdag gsum //
T02TD2151E:246a-32: rim gyis mnyam par dgod par bya //
T02TD2151E:246a-34: 'bru lnga sman lnga'i gtor ma dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-35: n'a ga ge sar kanda ka ri dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-36: n'a ga pushpa rgya mtsho dbu ba dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-37: chu srin sder mo dbang po lag pa dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-38: bal po'i se'u smyag shad lcug ma dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-39: n'i lotpa la 'dam bu'i rtsa ba dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-40: dar tshon sna lnga ras skud dmar po dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-41: li khri dmar po dang ni ga bur shel //
T02TD2151E:246a-42: pu shel tse dang ljon shing 'dam bu tshal //
T02TD2151E:246a-43: dkar gsum mngar gsum 'bras chan khur ba'o //
T02TD2151E:246a-46: gru bzhi sgo bzhi bhr'um las ni//
T02TD2151E:246a-48: phu:las glu brgyad klu chen te //
T02TD2151E:246a-49: 'khor yang de bzhin bskyed byas nas //
T02TD2151E:246a-50: gtso bo sgrub thabs las gsungs bzhin //
T02TD2151E:246a-51: spyan drangs bstim pa la sogs kyis //
T02TD2151E:246a-52: klu la sogs pa de bzhin dgug / aom rgya mtsho chen po'i klong dkyil nas //
T02TD2151E:246a-53: gtsug na rin chen klu yi rje //
T02TD2151E:246a-54: nor rgyas bu dang dung skyong dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-55: dga' bo dang ni 'jog po dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-56: padma dang ni chu lha dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-57: stobs kyi rgyu dang ma dros dang //
T02TD2151E:246a-58: klu chen brgyad po 'khor dang bcas //
T02TD2151E:246a-59: gnas 'dir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
T02TD2151E:246a-60: rgyal rigs dang ni bram ze'i rigs //
T02TD2151E:246a-61: rje rigs dang ni gdol ba'i rigs //
T02TD2151E:246a-62: gnas 'dir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol//
T02TD2151E:246b-0: @246b klu ban gnyan dang sa bdag tshogs //
T02TD2151E:246b-2: gnas 'dir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
T02TD2151E:246b-3: me tog la sogs mchod pa lnga //
T02TD2151E:246b-5: gtor ma rnams kyang so sor dbul //
T02TD2151E:246b-6: n'a ga ge sar sman gyi mchog / sngags dang phyag rgyas byin brlabs nas //
T02TD2151E:246b-8: klu chen brgyad la mchod pa dbul //
T02TD2151E:246b-9: sngon gyi dam tshig slar dul la //
T02TD2151E:246b-10: zhe rings dug las slar du la zhig / kanda ka ri n'a ga pushpa dang //
T02TD2151E:246b-11: rgya mtsho dbu bchu srin snger mo dang //
T02TD2151E:246b-12: dbang bo lag ba n'a ga ge sar dang //
T02TD2151E:246b-13: bal po se'u smyag shad lhug ma dang //
T02TD2151E:246b-14: n'i la autpal 'dam bu'i nags tshal dang //
T02TD2151E:246b-15: dar tshon sna lnga'i ras skud dmar po dang //
T02TD2151E:246b-16: li khri dmar po ga bur shal dang ni //
T02TD2151E:246b-17: pu shel rtse dang dung g-yas 'khyil ba dang //
T02TD2151E:246b-18: shu dag dkar po snying ni zho sha dang //
T02TD2151E:246b-19: mkhal ma zho sha stag pa'i shun pa dang //
T02TD2151E:246b-20: seng ldeng dkar dmar klu sman sna tshogs kyis //
T02TD2151E:246b-21: klu rnams kun la rab tu mchod par bya //
T02TD2151E:246b-22: mchod pa phul nas bzlas pa bya //
T02TD2151E:246b-23: aom n'a ga ha ra ha ra n'a ga phu //
T02TD2151E:246b-24: pra ha ra pra ha ra n'a ga phu //
T02TD2151E:246b-25: tshinda tshinda n'a ga phu hri da ya ni phu /
T02TD2151E:246b-26: bhinda bhinda n'a ga dha ma ni phu /
T02TD2151E:246b-27: bi si ma ta n'a ga sha r'i ra ni phu /
T02TD2151E:246b-28: bhinda bhinda n'a ga dha ma ni phu /
T02TD2151E:246b-29: bi si ma ta n'a ga sha r'i ra ni phu /
T02TD2151E:246b-30: bi spho ta ya n'a ga na ya ni phu /
T02TD2151E:246b-31: n'a ga bi d'a ra na ya phu /
T02TD2151E:246b-32: n'a ga kro dha na ya phu sv'a h'a /
T02TD2151E:246b-33: aom aa nanda ya h'um n'am h'um sv'a ha /
T02TD2151E:246b-34: aom b'a su ki h'um n'am h'um sv'a h'a /
T02TD2151E:246b-35: aom ta kasha ka h'um n'am h'um sv'a h'a /
T02TD2151E:246b-36: aom padma h'um n'am h'um sv'a h'a /
T02TD2151E:246b-37: aom ma h'a padma h'um n'am h'um sv'a h'a /
T02TD2151E:246b-38: aom sha kha p'a la h'um n'am h'um sv'a h'a /
T02TD2151E:246b-39: aom karko ta h'um n'um h'um sv'a h'a /
T02TD2151E:246b-40: aom aa na wa ta t'um n'am h'um sv'a 'a /
T02TD2151E:246b-41: aom n'a ka ku la tsa tva ri sh'a nti sv'a h'a /
T02TD2151E:246b-42: aom n'a ga pra ti spho ta ya sv'a h'a /
T02TD2151E:246b-43: ao n'a ga pra panytsa bu nye ba sv'a h'a /
T02TD2151E:246b-44: aom ta th'a ga ta hri da ya h'um sv'a h'a /
T02TD2151E:246b-45: aom ta th'a ga ta hri da ya tsa le tsa le h'um phat /
T02TD2151E:246b-46: kun la brgya brgya bzlas par bya //
T02TD2151E:246b-47: gtsug na yid bzhin nor bu can //
T02TD2151E:246b-48: mig ne gdengs pa lto 'phye'i rigs //
T02TD2151E:246b-49: klu chen brgyad ro mthong ba'i dug / bzod dka'i dug rnams phyir phyung shig / lus chen mgo bo tha dad pa'i //
T02TD2151E:246b-50: zhe sdang drag po rgyas pa yi //
T02TD2151E:246b-51: rigs bzhi klu rgyal yid kyi dung //
T02TD2151E:246b-52: bzod dka'i dug rnams phyir phyung shig / gsher la gnas pa mdzangs pa'i rigs //
T02TD2151E:246b-53: gtsang ma phal la gnod mi byed //
T02TD2151E:246b-54: klu bran 'bum sde reg ba'i dug / bzod dka'i dug rnams phyir phyung shig / zhe rings nag po bya lo song rigs //
T02TD2151E:246b-55: rmig bzhi lcags las na bun 'thibs //
T02TD2151E:246b-56: gnyen chen 'bum sde kha blangs dug / bzod dka'i dug rnams phyir phyung shig / dman pa'i cha 'dzin zhe sdang can //
T02TD2151E:247a-2: sa bdag 'bum sde mche ba'i dug / bzod dka'i dug rnams phyir phyung shig / dregs pa zhe sdang 'bar ba yi //
T02TD2151E:247a-3: glen pa brgyal mthu bo che //
T02TD2151E:247a-5: bzod dka'i dug rnams phyir phyung shig / sbyor gzhan rab tu khros pa'i po nya ni //
T02TD2151E:247a-6: sprul pa 'bum sde 'gro ba'i gnod pa skyel //
T02TD2151E:247a-7: sman dang sngags dang phyag rgya ting 'dzin gyis //
T02TD2151E:247a-8: bzod dka'i dug rnams phyir phyung zhig / de ltar bsnyen pa snong song bas //
T02TD2151E:247a-9: mchog tu sgrub pos dug phyung nas //
T02TD2151E:247a-10: rmi ltas rim pa so sor gsal //
T02TD2151E:247a-11: thub rtags byung na rdzas rnams ni //
T02TD2151E:247a-12: rten yod gnas su spa bar bya'o //
T02TD2151E:247a-13: gal te mi thub rtags byung nas//
T02TD2151E:247a-14: cho 'phrul drag po ston byed na //
T02TD2151E:247a-16: bsad pa'i las gyi sbyor ba ni //
T02TD2151E:247a-17: 'khor lo chen po la brten nas //
T02TD2151E:247a-18: klu grub dkyil 'khor shar phyogs su //
T02TD2151E:247a-19: thabs bzlog pa yi las bya ste //
T02TD2151E:247a-20: byang du gsad pa'i las bya'o //
T02TD2151E:247a-22: pra ram dzva la dzva la phat phat /
T02TD2151E:247a-23: shad shang shig shig phat phat /
T02TD2151E:247a-25: rigs bzhi klu la mnan pa bya //
T02TD2151E:247a-26: r'a dza ku le'i them pa'am //
T02TD2151E:247a-27: yang na sgrub khang them 'og tu //
T02TD2151E:247a-28: dbyar gyi khyim gsum tha ma la //
T02TD2151E:247a-29: drug gnyis bzhi yi nyin phyed na //
T02TD2151E:247a-30: shin tu dam par sba bar bya //
T02TD2151E:247a-31: rgya gram 'bar bas steng nas mnan //
T02TD2151E:247a-32: ji ltar bstan pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
T02TD2151E:247a-33: ri rab glang la bskor nas ni //
T02TD2151E:247a-34: bskal pa'i mtha' ru mnan par bsam //
T02TD2151E:247a-35: mthu stobs chen po'i nga ro yis //
T02TD2151E:247a-36: phreng ba'i sngags ni rab bzlas shing //
T02TD2151E:247a-37: rgya gram 'bar bas stang stabs bya //
T02TD2151E:247a-38: mos pa rang 'dod lha mnyes te //
T02TD2151E:247a-39: sgrub pas mngon sum snang bar mdzad //
T02TD2151E:247a-40: rtsol ba drag pos rtog pa'i nang las thar//
T02TD2151E:247a-41: yun du ma btang ngang ldan ngang bsrings na //
T02TD2151E:247a-42: taksha ka yis bzung bar gyur pa yang //
T02TD2151E:247a-43: zla ba drug gis bzlog 'gyur the tshom med //
T02TD2151E:247a-44: gang zhig rang sems dpang du btsugs nas ni //
T02TD2151E:247a-45: the tshom med par rtag tu ma brjed na //
T02TD2151E:247a-46: rtog pa'i nad las thar cing dngos grub 'byung bar nges //
T02TD2151E:247a-47: 'gro la brtse bas klu sgrub 'khrul 'khor brtsams //
T02TD2151E:247a-48: 'ad las bsod nams dag rtsa ca yad pa //
T02TD2151E:247a-49: gang mas rtog pa'i nad las thar gyur nas //
T02TD2151E:247a-50: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi zhal mthong shog / rin chen dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal nas //
T02TD2151E:247b-0: dngos grub sdug @247b bsngal thams cad zhi bar shog / slob dpon dza' ba ri pas mdzad pa'i klu sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
T02TD2151E:247b-2: // / bal po'i pandi ta de ba p'u rnam ti dang /
T02TD2151E:247b-3: lo ts'a ba dge slong chos kyi bzang pos bsgyur ba'o//
